- I'm never getting
out of this place.

1221
00:47:40.399 --> 00:47:42.860
- This means you're clear
for takeoff.

1222
00:47:42.943 --> 00:47:46.614
Nothing here we can't handle
with night shift coming in.

1223
00:47:46.697 --> 00:47:48.991
- Yeah. right.
Free to go.

1224
00:47:49.075 --> 00:47:51.702
Uh. hey. I told you
I would get you up there.

1225
00:47:51.786 --> 00:47:54.205
and I promise I'm not leaving
until you're back

1226
00:47:54.246 --> 00:47:55.873
and sent packing.

1227
00:47:55.915 --> 00:47:57.500
- Robby. buddy.
you got me to come in.

1228
00:47:57.583 --> 00:47:59.210
got me to take my tests.

1229
00:47:59.251 --> 00:48:01.379
You don't got to babysit me.
That's why I have a nurse.

1230
00:48:01.462 --> 00:48:03.547
What's your name. sweetheart?
- Nurse Vivi. sir.

1231
00:48:03.631 --> 00:48:05.549
- That's what I have
the lovely Nurse Vivi here for.

1232
00:48:05.591 --> 00:48:07.510
- This will not take very long.

1233
00:48:07.593 --> 00:48:09.887
- [laughs]
Where have I heard that before?

1234
00:48:09.929 --> 00:48:11.389
- Hey.

1235
00:48:11.430 --> 00:48:13.766
So. uh. this is it. huh?

1236
00:48:13.849 --> 00:48:15.935
- Uh. yeah.

1237
00:48:16.018 --> 00:48:18.270
Don't let the place burn down.

1238
00:48:20.272 --> 00:48:22.024
- You know...

1239
00:48:22.066 --> 00:48:24.902
in a previous life. I had a lot
of friends who liked to see

1240
00:48:24.985 --> 00:48:27.196
how close the edge was...

1241
00:48:27.279 --> 00:48:30.574
as if it was a challenge
they were called to meet.

1242
00:48:30.658 --> 00:48:33.702
Trouble is.
they all inevitably found it.

1243
00:48:36.080 --> 00:48:37.540
- Okay.

1244
00:48:39.917 --> 00:48:41.210
- I'm just picking up

1245
00:48:41.293 --> 00:48:43.212
on a weird vibe
from you today is all.

1246
00:48:43.254 --> 00:48:47.299
- [laughing] Yeah. well.
it's been a weird day.

1247
00:48:52.304 --> 00:48:54.223
- You leaving?
- Uh. yeah.

1248
00:48:54.306 --> 00:48:57.184
My shift is over. and I ain't
getting paid to be here.

1249
00:48:57.268 --> 00:48:59.395
Quite literally the opposite.
in fact.

1250
00:48:59.478 --> 00:49:01.230
- Well. I don't know
if you noticed.

1251
00:49:01.272 --> 00:49:04.108
but we're sort of. uh.
in disaster mode here still.

1252
00:49:04.150 --> 00:49:06.735
We put in the extra time
if we're needed.

1253
00:49:08.696 --> 00:49:13.159
- You know 62% of ED docs
report suffering from burnout?

1254
00:49:13.242 --> 00:49:15.077
- Painfully aware.
- Mm.

1255
00:49:15.161 --> 00:49:17.621
So maybe all you lunatics
need to learn

1256
00:49:17.705 --> 00:49:21.459
how to set some boundaries.
like me.

1257
00:49:21.542 --> 00:49:24.170
Well. see you tomorrow. Doc.

1258
00:49:25.963 --> 00:49:27.965
Good luck in there.
Sorry about the mess.

1259
00:49:28.048 --> 00:49:29.258
- "Mess"?

1260
00:49:29.341 --> 00:49:32.136
[indistinct chatter]

1261
00:49:32.219 --> 00:49:33.721
[bell dings]

1262
00:49:33.804 --> 00:49:35.264
Yup.

1263
00:49:35.347 --> 00:49:37.057
- Incoming.
- Head trauma.

1264
00:49:37.141 --> 00:49:38.934
Unwitnessed fall
from the warehouse catwalk

1265
00:49:39.018 --> 00:49:42.229
where he works
as a security guard.

1266
00:49:42.313 --> 00:49:43.981
- Oh. my God.

1267
00:49:44.023 --> 00:49:45.441
Orlando.

1268
00:49:45.524 --> 00:49:48.027
He left five hours ago.

1269
00:49:49.305 --> 00:50:49.320
